gap_analysis_prompt_response.OverallAssessment: The candidate demonstrates strong backend development capabilities with 60% more experience than required (8+ years vs 5+ years). Their Python and FastAPI expertise directly matches core requirements. However, significant gaps exist in full-stack capabilities, particularly React frontend development and DevOps practices (Kubernetes, CI/CD). With only 38% keyword coverage, the candidate currently profiles as a backend specialist rather than a full-stack developer. To be competitive, they would need 3-6 months of focused learning in React and Kubernetes. Immediate resume improvements highlighting any frontend experience and cloud transferable skills could increase their match to 50-60%. The candidate has strong potential but needs to bridge the full-stack gap.
